## Limitations

The analysis is limited by the availability of recent data and the evolving nature of sharp power strategies. The concept of sharp power is relatively new, and its implications are still being studied. Additionally, the reliance on publicly available sources may not capture the full scope of covert activities associated with sharp power. Further research and longitudinal studies are needed to fully understand the long-term impact of sharp power on global politics.